HEADWORD: Frondose
<hw>Fron*dose"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>frondosus</ets> leafy.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>Frond bearing; resembling a frond; having a simple expansion not
separable into stem and leaves.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Leafy.</def>
